    <summary>The bestest free-to-win rhythm game. Rhythm is just a click away!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="ru">Наилучшая бесплатная ритм-игра. Ритм всего лишь в клике от тебя!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="it">Il miglior gioco di ritmo free-to-win. Il ritmo è solo ad un click di distanza!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="de">Das besteste free-to-play rhythmusspiel. Der rhythmus ist nur einen klick entfernt!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="hu">A legeslegjobb ingyen játszható ritmusjáték. A ritmus csak egy kattintásra van!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="ja">基本料無料で最高のリズムゲーム. リズムはもう、その指先に!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="pl">Darmowa gra rytmiczna. rytm jest tylko o klik stąd!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="fr">Le meilleur jeu de rythme free-to-win. Rhythm is just a click away!</summary>
    <summary xml:lang="es">El mejor juego de ritmo gratis. El ritmo está a un solo clic de distancia</summary>
    <description>
        <p>Open source rhythm game written in C# and inspired by Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan</p>
        <p>
            Attention: Unofficial build. Please report all bugs found on https://github.com/kowalski7cc/sh.ppy.osu (if you think they may be related to a flatpak)
        </p>
        A free-to-win rhythm game. Rhythm is just a click away!

        The future of osu! and the beginning of an open era! Currently known by and released under the codename "lazer". As in sharper than cutting-edge.
    </description>
